{"1":{"w":[{"b":"0.1","h":"0.45","c":"وَالْعَادِيَاتِ","d":"ِtَٰyِdَٰʿعْlٱَw","e":"wal-ʿādiyāti"},{"b":"1.8","h":"3.19","c":"ضَبْحًا","d":"āًḥْbَḍ","e":"ḍabḥan"}],"a":{"g":"By the racers, panting,"}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.5","c":"فَالْمُورِيَاتِ","d":"ِtَٰyِrwُmْlٱَf","e":"fal-mūriyāti"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.18","c":"قَدْحًا","d":"āًḥْdَq","e":"qadḥan"}],"a":{"g":"And the producers of sparks [when] striking"}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.2","c":"فَالْمُغِيرَاتِ","d":"ِtَٰryِغُmْlٱَf","e":"fal-mughīrāti"},{"b":"1.6","h":"2.92","c":"صُبْحًا","d":"āًḥْbُṣ","e":"ṣub'ḥan"}],"a":{"g":"And the chargers at dawn,"}},"4":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.3","c":"فَأَثَرْنَ","d":"َnْrَhtَaʾَf","e":"fa-atharna"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.97","c":"بِهِ","d":"ۦِhِb","e":"bihi"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.13","c":"نَقْعًا","d":"āًʿعْqَn","e":"naqʿan"}],"a":{"g":"Stirring up thereby [clouds of] dust,","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                وكذلك قد يقع الأبهام في الحروف مثل قوله عز وجل ﴿ فأثرن به نقعا فوسطن به جمعا ﴾ فالهاء الأولى كناية عن الحوافر وهي الموريات أي أثرن بالحوافر نقعا. والثانية كناية عن الإغارة وهي المغيرات صبحا فوسطن به جمعا جمع المشركون فأغاروا بجمعهم\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, ambiguity may also occur in the letters, such as the saying of the Almighty, the Exalted: \"So they stirred up thereby a cloud [of dust], and they stormed thereby into the assembly [fa-atharna bihi naq'an fa-wasatna bihi jam'an].\" The first 'him' [bihi] is a metaphor for the hooves, which are the igniters [al-mūriyāt], meaning they stirred up a cloud [of dust] with the hooves. And the second 'him' [bihi] is a metaphor for the raid, which are the raiders at dawn [al-mughīrāt ṣubḥan], so they stormed with it into the assembly, the assembly of the polytheists, and they raided with their assembly.\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"5":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.35","c":"فَوَسَطْنَ","d":"َnْṭَsَwَf","e":"fawasaṭna"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.97","c":"بِهِ","d":"ۦِhِb","e":"bihi"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.11","c":"جَمْعًا","d":"āًʿعْmَjg","e":"jamʿan"}],"a":{"g":"Arriving thereby in the center collectively,"}},"6":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.55","c":"إِنَّ","d":"َّnِiʾ","e":"inna"},{"b":"1.1","h":"1.92","c":"الْإِنْسَانَ","d":"َnَٰsnِiʾْlٱ","e":"l-insāna"},{"b":"3.4","h":"4.51","c":"لِرَبِّهِ","d":"ۦِhِّbَrِl","e":"lirabbihi"},{"b":"4.7","h":"6.7","c":"لَكَنُودٌ","d":"ٌdwُnَkَl","e":"lakanūdun"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed mankind, to his Lord, is ungrateful."}},"7":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.45","c":"وَإِنَّهُ","d":"ۥُhَّnِiʾَw","e":"wa-innahu"},{"b":"1.8","h":"2.52","c":"عَلَى","d":"ٰàَlَʿع","e":"ʿalā"},{"b":"2.5","h":"3.56","c":"ذَلِكَ","d":"َkِlَٰhd","e":"dhālika"},{"b":"3.5","h":"5.14","c":"لَشَهِيدٌ","d":"ٌdyِhَhsَl","e":"lashahīdun"}],"a":{"g":"And indeed, he is to that a witness."}},"8":{"w":[{"b":"0.08","h":"0.51","c":"وَإِنَّهُ","d":"ۥُhَّnِiʾَw","e":"wa-innahu"},{"b":"2.0","h":"2.73","c":"لِحُبِّ","d":"ِّbُḥِl","e":"liḥubbi"},{"b":"2.9","h":"4.06","c":"الْخَيْرِ","d":"ِrْyَhkْlٱ","e":"l-khayri"},{"b":"3.8","h":"5.51","c":"لَشَدِيدٌ","d":"ٌdyِdَhsَl","e":"lashadīdun"}],"a":{"g":"And indeed he is, in love of wealth, intense."}},"9":{"w":[{"b":"0.1","h":"0.5","c":"أَفَلَا","d":"āَlَfَaʾ","e":"afalā"},{"b":"0.88","h":"1.7","c":"يَعْلَمُ","d":"ُmَlْʿعَy","e":"yaʿlamu"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.11","c":"إِذَا","d":"āَhdِiʾ","e":"idhā"},{"b":"2.4","h":"4.18","c":"بُعْثِرَ","d":"َrِhtْʿعُb","e":"buʿ'thira"},{"b":"3.3","h":"5.59","c":"مَا","d":"āَm","e":"mā"},{"b":"3.7","h":"6.34","c":"فِي","d":"àِf","e":"fī"},{"b":"3.9","h":"6.75","c":"الْقُبُورِ","d":"ِrwُbُqْlٱ","e":"l-qubūri"}],"a":{"g":"But does he not know that when the contents of the graves are scattered"}},"10":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.36","c":"وَحُصِّلَ","d":"َlِّṣُḥَw","e":"waḥuṣṣila"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.96","c":"مَا","d":"āَm","e":"mā"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.7","c":"فِي","d":"àِf","e":"fī"},{"b":"1.6","h":"3.08","c":"الصُّدُورِ","d":"ِrwُdُّṣlٱ","e":"l-ṣudūri"}],"a":{"g":"And that within the breasts is obtained,"}},"11":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.65","c":"إِنَّ","d":"َّnِiʾ","e":"inna"},{"b":"1.3","h":"1.76","c":"رَبَّهُمْ","d":"mُhَّbَr","e":"rabbahum"},{"b":"3.1","h":"4","c":"بِهِمْ","d":"ْmِhِb","e":"bihim"},{"b":"3.8","h":"4.98","c":"يَوْمَئِذٍ","d":"ٍhdِyʾَmْwَy","e":"yawma-idhin"},{"b":"5.1","h":"6.87","c":"لَخَبِيرٌ","d":"ٌۢryِbَhkَّl","e":"lakhabīrun"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, their Lord with them, that Day, is [fully] Acquainted."}}}